name: IowaCityEvents
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Do you want to know what events are going on in Iowa City and the University of Iowa? Well now you can with Alexa! This Flash Briefing skill collects events from various sources. To get started, go to the Flash Briefing settings and choose what events types and sources you are interested in.

The following sources are supported:
Think Iowa City,
University of Iowa Sustainability,
University of Iowa School of Music,
University of Iowa Arts,
Hancher,
CAB,
University of Iowa College of Pharmacy,
University of Iowa Recreational Services,
University of Iowa College of Engineering,
University of Iowa Gradate College,
University of Iowa Tippie College of Business,
University of Iowa Research and Economic Development

For more University of Iowa feeds, please contact the developer.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
